<div id="review_2078172722" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2078172722" />
    <a title="Jessa" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/21712829-jessa"><img alt="Jessa" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1429843826p2/21712829.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2078172722?book_show_action=true">Jul 31, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Jessa" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Jessa" href="/user/show/21712829-jessa">Jessa</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/21712829-jessa?shelf=beta-hero">beta-hero</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/21712829-jessa?shelf=friends-to-lovers">friends-to-lovers</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/21712829-jessa?shelf=babes-with-disabilities">babes-with-disabilities</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/21712829-jessa?shelf=historical-romance">historical-romance</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/21712829-jessa?shelf=book-boyfriend">book-boyfriend</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/21712829-jessa?shelf=plain-jane-or-jimmy">plain-jane-or-jimmy</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2078172722" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer195931083430478171">It&apos;s so rare to find a hero who is truly just average in looks and stature rather than some daunting perfect specimen, especially in historicals. And while I&apos;m just as guilty as loving those perfect men, there&apos;s something so wonderful about someone like Hartley, Lord Carew. He&apos;s so beautiful on the inside and I fell in love with him. Sam did too, eventually, but the journey was rough because the main couple is just so naive. Hartley thought Sam was in love with him but she married him because he</span>
  <span id="freeText195931083430478171" style="display:none">It's so rare to find a hero who is truly just average in looks and stature rather than some daunting perfect specimen, especially in historicals. And while I'm just as guilty as loving those perfect men, there's something so wonderful about someone like Hartley, Lord Carew. He's so beautiful on the inside and I fell in love with him. Sam did too, eventually, but the journey was rough because the main couple is just so naive. Hartley thought Sam was in love with him but she married him because he felt like warmth and safety and friendship. They both thought they were on the same page until it all came to a truly angsty and stressful head...which is the drama I thrive on. <br /><br />Loved this one!</span>
  <a data-text-id="195931083430478171" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


